{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Preheat oven to 200°C. Line a baking tray (30 x 40 cm) with baking paper and set aside.","Place onions, oil, garlic and chilli in mixing bowl then chop <nobr>3 sec\/speed 7<\/nobr>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then sauté <nobr>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<\/nobr>.","Add tinned tomatoes, cayenne pepper, paprika and salt. Place Varoma dish into position and weigh potatoes into it. Secure Varoma lid and cook <nobr>20 min\/100°C\/speed 1<\/nobr>. Set Varoma aside and insert measuring cup, then blend <nobr>30 sec\/speed 5<\/nobr>. Transfer sauce into a bowl and cover to keep warm.","Place potatoes onto prepared baking tray and top with sliced chorizo. Bake for 15 minutes (200°C). Remove from oven and stir potatoes and chorizo to ensure even cooking. Return tray to the oven and bake for a further 25-30 minutes (200°C), or until potatoes are golden and chorizo is sizzling.","Transfer potatoes and chorizo into a serving bowl and serve sauce warm on the side."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["60 g red onions","1 tbsp olive oil","2 garlic cloves","½ - 1 fresh red chilli, deseeded if preferred and halved","400 g tinned chopped tomatoes","1 pinch ground cayenne pepper","1 pinch ground smoked paprika","¼ - ½ tsp fine sea salt, to taste","800 - 850 g small potatoes, peeled and cut in pieces (2-3 cm)","500 g chorizo, thinly sliced"]}],"id":"r123517","imageLink":"https:\/\/1.bp.blogspot.com\/-qobSm_e4ao8\/XZMvOoCGcGI\/AAAAAAAAaPM\/uqs7xNRMBZElTaCb03oKIYKdErJeXu0HwCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ayxpBKZh7JlwUGaz.png","title":"Patatas Bravas with Chorizo","publishedAt":"2017-04-24T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"11 g","fat":"10.5 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"13 g","calories":"828 kJ \/ 197 kcal"},"usefulItems":"baking tray (30 x 40 cm), baking paper, silicone spatula, oven","hintsAndTricks":["This is a classic tapas dish served throughout Spain. Enjoy as the start to a Tapas themed menu or simply as a nibble at your next party."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","1h 20m","10 portions"]}